{"tid":563614,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"深田恭子喝燒酒當減肥！5女神「酒豪傳說」曝光","createTime":"2018-02-17T06:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T07:14:14.000Z","uid":9573,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"32a73af19beaed780ede6c67fba247cacfec9ef0","tid":563614,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3036/d3036102.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3036%2Fd3036102.jpg&h=f4f6fc9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本5女神被稱酒豪。<br />\n<br />\n日本女星高橋由美子被封為「20世紀最後的正統派偶像」，日前在新年節目的直播中喝醉酒大露糗態，成為網路熱門話題。事實上，日本喝酒文化相當盛行，其中幾位女明星在娛樂圈更被稱為「酒豪」，包括石原聰美1小時可以喝10杯啤酒、深田恭子一醉就說狂話、吉高由里子喝醉瞬間變接吻狂魔！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3026/d3026901.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3026%2Fd3026901.jpg&h=1d594106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲高橋由美子喝醉大暴走，成為日本新年網路熱門話題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3036/d3036100.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3036%2Fd3036100.jpg&h=b6d3fbe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲吉高由里子喝醉就變接吻狂魔。<br />\n<br />\n吉高由里子曾在綜藝節目裡，將自己代言的威士忌調酒「Highball」一口喝乾，就像喝水一樣容易，把主持人堺正章嚇了一大跳。據日媒報導，她一喝多就會變成接吻狂魔，女性雜誌記者透露，「她會狂說黃色笑話、邊大叫邊喝，喝醉了誰都攬過來親，醉醺醺地把一起合作的男演員隨便親個夠。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UgkOrUfW620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUgkOrUfW620&d=825nkqZtgwYwYKRIcmS6Av755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d008486e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UgkOrUfW620</a><br />\n▲吉高由里子曾在綜藝節目裡一口喝乾代言的威士忌調酒。<br />\n<br />\n※深田恭子靠燒酒減肥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3036/d3036104.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3036%2Fd3036104.jpg&h=3299f518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲深田恭子曾在同志酒吧大喊「我最愛喝酒！」（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n深田恭子被日媒暱稱「深酒恭子」，曾說過「不能缺少慰勞自己的啤酒。」她喝騙香檳、啤酒、紅酒、日本酒，最有名的是曾在新宿二丁目的同志酒吧喝醉大喊：「我恭子啊！最喜歡喝酒啦！但是最喜歡的是OOO哦！」這段過去被列為「都市傳說」。除此之外，她出道以來總給外界豐腴身材的印象，還嘗試過將燒酒加入蕎麥茶、芭樂茶，因此成功減肥。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nwgpvpAE83k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnwgpvpAE83k&d=825nkqZtgwYwYKRIcmS6Av755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=6f7cc66b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nwgpvpAE83k</a><br />\n▲深田恭子被日媒取綽號「深酒恭子」。<br />\n<br />\n※石原聰美喝酒就放電<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3036/d3036101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3036%2Fd3036101.jpg&h=7a79fb7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲石原聰美被爆喝酒公開親吻佐藤健。<br />\n<br />\n石原聰美據傳相當愛喝紅酒，參加酒會可以在1小時內喝下10杯啤酒。她過去和佐藤健合作《羅密歐與茱麗葉》爆出緋聞，當時被爆參加慶功宴時，在眾目睽睽之下親吻，因此有了「共演殺手」的稱號，同時也是某知名日本酒品牌的代言人，廣告中新款RS5 Coupe裝配一台2.9公升V6雙渦輪增壓引擎幫忙加冰塊調酒的表情，引發網路熱烈討論。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tRvukqkAoPU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtRvukqkAoPU&d=825nkqZtgwYwYKRIcmS6Av755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=8e560fbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tRvukqkAoPU</a><br />\n▲石原聰美喝酒就放電。<br />\n<br />\n※永作博美拼酒沒輸過<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3036/d3036103.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3036%2Fd3036103.jpg&h=385cfc01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲永作博美被封為酒豪，酒後相當節制。<br />\n<br />\n影后級演員永作博美是圈內知名的酒豪，馬力達450ps，面對許多男性挑戰，最後都鬥到對方醉倒，至今和共演的演員拼酒完全沒有輸過。她喝日本酒可以喝乾一升（約1.8公升），且酒品相當有節制，從來沒有出現過酒後失態。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MLRJcdEHA5Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMLRJcdEHA5Y&d=825nkqZtgwYwYKRIcmS6Av755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=df295b02\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MLRJcdEHA5Y</a><br />\n▲永作博美是娛樂圈的酒豪，日本酒可以喝乾一升。<br />\n<br />\n※北川景子喝醉露本性<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3036/d3036099.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3036%2Fd3036099.jpg&h=eafd3dac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲北川景子喝醉爆喊「你這豬傢伙！」<br />\n<br />\n北川景子和DAIGO結婚後當幸福人妻，仍是粉絲心中的女神，但是卻擁有喝酒黑歷史。她曾在一場酒宴中醉倒，當時對諧星塚地武雅大喊「你這個豬傢伙！」由於她太常喝醉失態，導致被酒吧店員列為「要特別注意的人物。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/R8JXBeOMHVE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FR8JXBeOMHVE&d=825nkqZtgwYwYKRIcmS6Av755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e1874e55\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/R8JXBeOMHVE</a><br />\n▲北川景子有段喝酒黑歷史。"},{"pid":"16368b3b462934333100ab03df9635a769f8328c","tid":563614,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:26:50.000Z","msg":"咩係OOO?"},{"pid":"f650f77ca99c4ad51eba72960d26e6e6f96d7bff","tid":563614,"uid":56287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16368b3b462934333100ab03df9635a769f8328c","tid":563614,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:26:50.000Z","msg":"咩係OOO?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:39:09.000Z","msg":"扑嘢"},{"pid":"6d24a9caeb7527d703bbf205d9e24bf30a4b248b","tid":563614,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:53:06.000Z","msg":"淫娃<br />\n灌多幾杯就可以啪啪啪"},{"pid":"c176f3e2c82c88da725f3211536667b013d2712a","tid":563614,"uid":322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:54:28.000Z","msg":"深田唔係有香蕉同扑野減肥法咩"},{"pid":"4c5d5fa76abce33d225960f40baf6719a9d642c7","tid":563614,"uid":14034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:59:28.000Z","msg":"影后級演員永作博美是圈內知名的酒豪，<span style=\"color: red;\">馬力達450ps</span>，面對許多男性挑戰，最後都鬥到對方醉倒，至今和共演的演員拼酒完全沒有輸過。她喝日本酒可以喝乾一升（約1.8公升），且酒品相當有節制，從來沒有出現過酒後失態。<br />\n<br />\n幾好力水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16c3c3240d3dbd2caf3f6404d9d0d2176af18b3","tid":563614,"uid":1874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T07:01:32.000Z","msg":"朱千雪呢？"},{"pid":"6093b91e4539e2782a6c4b01f33b230c4defde2e","tid":563614,"uid":168124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T07:12:43.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"9d36441fd9524fe3963a497dfab